""" 00 Transformations """

Transform each set of lines using the specified rule.

========
Rule:

a
=>
a += a % 3

--------

vim
tutor
apple
pear
banana

========
Rule:

C.a = a
=>
C.set_a(a)

--------

C.vim = vim
C.tutor = tutor
C.apple = apple
C.pear = pear

========
Rule:

a = c - b
=>
a = -b + c

--------

vim = text - hassle
profit = revenue - cost
taxes = government - anarchy
